name: FOAMPOSITE IPHONE 5 CASE METALLIC PURPLE
description:
This is an iPhone 5 Case made of real foam material in a metallic purple color. The Nike Foamposite has become one of the most sought after shoe models of all time and have reached their all time peak of popularity. This iPhone 5 case is molded to not only resemble, but also feel, like one of your favorite shoes. If you're a foam-head and own an iPhone 5 then you NEED to be rocking this amazing accessory.

This case is mostly decorative and although it will protect your iPhone 5 from bumps and scratches, it is not meant to withstand a hard drop.
